  <title>U.S. Counties (Generalized)</title>
  <abstract>U.S. Counties (Generalized) represents the counties of the United States in the 50 states and the District of Columbia.

U.S. Counties (Generalized) provides 2010 U.S. Census demographic information and generalized county boundaries to improve draw performance and be used effectively at a national level.</abstract>
